# Exclude from the packaged .vsix — keep installs lean

.vscode/**
.github/**
src/**
.gitignore
.eslintrc*
tsconfig.json
*.map
node_modules/**

# Keep these IN the package:
# out/**         ← compiled JS (required)
# package.json   ← required
# README.md      ← shown in marketplace
# CHANGELOG.md   ← shown in marketplace
# images/**      ← extension icon
# ivr-helpers.js     ← shipped as starter template
# ivr-payload.json   ← shipped as starter template
# example-script.hbs ← shipped as example
# settings-example.jsonc ← shipped as reference
